node.text: Despite the incredible lows there were some high points. The @toryburchfoundation #EmbraceAmbition Summit was last March and I am incredibly proud of our team and how they pivoted and have risen to meet all of the extraordinary challenges that came our way.  Resilience, creativity, love and optimism are some of the adjectives that come to mind- thank you. Looking forward to a better 2021! Happy New Year! 🧡

node.text: This Women’s Entrepreneurship Day, my friend, stylist and entrepreneur @jasonbolden and I wanted to do something special to celebrate the resilience, creativity and generosity of women entrepreneurs in 2020. We are happy to introduce @toryburchfoundation Fellows – Ericka Lassair the founder of @divadawgtruck and Carolina Contreras the founder of @miss_rizos. It was great to catch up with Ericka and Carolina and thank you Jason!#EmbraceAmbition #WomensEntrepreneurshipDay

node.text: This Women’s Entrepreneurship Day, my friend, stylist and entrepreneur @jasonbolden and I wanted to do something special to celebrate the resilience, creativity and generosity of women entrepreneurs in 2020. We are happy to introduce @toryburchfoundation Fellows – Ericka Lassair the founder of @divadawgtruck and Carolina Contreras the founder of @miss_rizos. It was great to catch up with Ericka and Carolina and thank you Jason!#EmbraceAmbition #WomensEntrepreneurshipDay

node.text:
#ToryStories: our Fall ’21 collection through the lens of photographer of @satchellee. Lee selected six women to be photographed in their NYC homes, offices and neighborhoods. “This is a walking city. It's the walking city,” says Lee. “People can really see you and I think a question lots of New Yorkers ask themselves before they get dressed is, ‘How do I want to be seen?’”

Skateboarder and actress Ajani Russell, @ajvni, is wearing the English mohair pant, vest and men’s blazer with the Hank sneaker and #TMonogram jacquard shoulder bag

#ToryBurchFW21 #ToryBurch

node.text: The #TMonogram shoulder bag has a Seventies feel, with its structured shape and sporty webbing strap. Lined in soft microsuede, the interior has multiple pockets to organize your phone and other small essentials. Every detail is considered, with special attention to function and versatility. #ToryBurchFW21 #ToryBurch

node.text:
#ToryStories: our Fall ’21 collection through the lens of photographer of @satchellee. Lee selected six women to be photographed in their NYC homes, offices and neighborhoods. "I choose to photograph this group of women because they all inspire me. Not only are they beautiful but I get so hyped seeing young Black and Brown women doing their thing,” says Lee. “Life can be whatever you make of it, and it’s nice to be reminded of that by a group of extraordinary artists and entrepreneurs.”

Read more on #ToryDaily at the link in bio.

Filmmaker Tiye Amenechi, @biggtiye, wearing our printed tie-sleeve tunic dress, Hank sneaker and #TMonogram jacquard barrel.

#ToryBurchFW21 #ToryBurch

node.text: Classic American workwear reimagined. The #ToryBurchFW21 collection focuses on timeless pieces grounded in simplicity and ease. node.text: The #TMonogram Collection. When I started the company, we created a logo that was meant to be a graphic design element. A classic serif T and its mirror image encased in a circle, inspired by the geometry of Moroccan architecture and interiors by David Hicks. #ToryBurchFW21 #ToryBurch
